HEADWORD: Pigmentation
<hw>Pig`men*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>A deposition, esp. an excessive deposition,
of coloring matter; <as>as, <ex>pigmentation</ex> of the
liver</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pigmented</ent>⟦br⟧
